3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-live-off-grid-tiny-house-2024-2%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elive%20off-grid%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20West%20Virginia.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOur%20experience%20has%20been%20challenging%3A%20I%20felt%20lonely%20at%20first%2C%20and%20our%20home%20requires%20a%20lot%20of%20upkeep.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThat%20said%2C%20I%20love%20being%20among%20nature%2C%20and%20I've%20been%20able%20to%20save%20a%20lot%20of%20money.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20now-husband%20Scott%20and%20I%20fell%20in%20love%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-hiked-appalachian-trail-ran-out-of-water-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehiking%20the%20Appalachian%20Trail%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20college%20%E2%80%94%20and%20then%20spent%20the%20next%20few%20years%20fantasizing%20about%20a%20rural%2C%20nature-filled%2C%20off-grid%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20finished%20college%20in%202015%2C%20we%20finally%20had%20an%20opportunity%20to%20make%20that%20dream%20come%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20lived%20in%20the%20Northeast%20my%20whole%20life%20and%20met%20Scott%20in%20Vermont%2C%20but%20he%20grew%20up%20in%20rural%20West%20Virginia.%20When%20he%20inherited%20land%20there%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20make%20the%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20in%20West%20Virginia%2C%20we'd%20build%20a%20cabin%2C%20adopt%20a%20few%20rescue%20pets%2C%20raise%20chickens%20and%20bees%2C%20and%20live%20off-grid.%20We%20figured%20this%20lifestyle%20would%20be%20sustainable%20and%20budget-friendly%2C%20and%20after%20the%20Appalachian%20Trail%2C%20how%20hard%20could%20it%20be%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20didn't%20anticipate%20how%20isolated%20we'd%20feel%20at%20times%2C%20and%20how%20challenging%20it%20would%20be%20to%20care%20for%20our%20home%20%E2%80%94%20still%2C%20we'd%20make%20the%20choice%20again%20in%20a%20heartbeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2295ad864d-55c7-42ad-9500-8100fe0d6fb1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMoving%20800%20miles%20from%20home%20right%20after%20college%20was%20more%20difficult%20than%20I%20expected%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221836%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20woods%20near%20the%20writer's%20off-grid%20home%20in%20West%20Virginia.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68cc31c6183847aa39d7083c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221206%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20home%20is%20beautiful%2C%20but%20felt%20lonely%20at%20first.%3Cp%3EJordan%20Charbonneau%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20many%20amazing%20friends%20in%20high%20school%20and%20college%2C%20but%20I've%20never%20been%20a%20particularly%20outgoing%20person.%20Historically%2C%20I'd%20just%20meet%20people%20through%20classes%20and%20sports%20%E2%80%94%20I%20never%20really%20had%20to%20put%20myself%20out%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoving%20to%20a%20rural%20area%2C%20800%20miles%20from%20where%20I%20grew%20up%2C%20was%20lonelier%20than%20I%20thought%20it%20would%20be.%20I%20could%20no%20longer%20text%20a%20childhood%20friend%20or%20cousin%20to%20go%20on%20a%20quick%20hike%20or%20swim.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20neighbors%20who%20have%20become%20our%20friends%2C%20but%20they%20live%20anywhere%20from%20one%20to%20a%20few%20miles%20up%20or%20down%20our%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20rural%20location%20also%20made%20remote%20work%20the%20obvious%20choice%20for%20me%2C%20so%20I%20haven't%20really%20been%20able%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-friends-at-work-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eform%20friendships%20with%20coworkers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225fd647cd-5104-4048-b300-10aa9afccb77%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20learned%20that%20owning%20an%20off-grid%20cabin%20is%20like%20having%20a%20high-maintenance%20pet%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22810%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20writer's%20off-grid%2