for%20cocktails.%20A%20few%20have%20even%20made%20the%20trip%20up%20to%20visit%20our%20house%20on%20four-wheelers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20helped%20that%20Scott's%20friends%20and%20family%2C%20who%20live%20on%20our%20road%20(but%20on%20the%20grid)%2C%20were%20quick%20to%20offer%20me%20a%20seat%20at%20the%20table%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20I%20slowly%20gained%20confidence%20and%20started%20making%20a%20concerted%20effort%20to%20engage%20with%20the%20community.%20Now%2C%20I%20help%20to%20organize%20community%20plant%20swaps%2C%20attend%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarting-neighborhood-book-club-to-make-real-friends-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebook%20club%3C%2Fa%3E%20meetings%2C%20and%20network%20with%20other%20local%20writers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20it%20can%20be%20difficult%20to%20take%20care%20of%20our%20home%2C%20we%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20financial%20freedom%20%E2%80%94%20another%20highlight%20of%20living%20here.%20Our%20only%20home-related%20costs%20are%20%24120%20a%20month%20for%20internet%20and%20%2420%20for%20propane.%20We%20have%20no%20mortgage%2C%20electric%2C%20water%2C%20sewer%2C%20or%20gas%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20that%20our%20income%20stretches%20much%2C%20much%20further.%20Living%20off-grid%2C%20I%20was%20even%20able%20to%20pursue%20my%20writing%20full-time%20while%20we%20lived%20primarily%20on%20my%20self-employed%20husband's%20income%20for%20the%20first%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2292ae9417-952e-4933-a82a-85ade2fd1b75%5C%22%3EThe%20best%20part%20about%20our%20low%20cost%20of%20living%2C%20though%2C%20has%20been%20our%20ability%20to%20spend%20time%20with%20loved%20ones%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221698%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20writer%20with%20her%20mom%20in%20the%20woods.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68cc352457d362d375e86cdb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221166%5C%22%3E%3C