er.com%2Fgovernment-shutdown-stock-market-impact-history-sp500-bond-yields-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eshowdowns%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20sudden%20changes%20to%20rules%20for%20banks%20or%20businesses%20%E2%80%94%20slows%20lending%20and%20investment%20in%20the%20euro%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20post%2C%20co-authored%20by%20Anastasia%20Allayioti%2C%20an%20economist%20in%20the%20ECB's%20Monetary%20Policy%20Strategy%20Division%2C%20Caterina%20Mendicino%2C%20an%20advisor%20in%20the%20ECB's%20Monetary%20Analysis%20Division%2C%20and%20several%20colleagues%2C%20used%20euro-area%20data%20going%20back%20to%202003%20and%20a%20statistical%20model%20that%20tracks%20how%20shocks%20spread%20through%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20found%20that%20a%20rise%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-immigration-prices-manufacturing-tariffs-america-economy-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS%20policy%20uncertainty%3C%2Fa%3E%20reduces%20euro-area%20loan%20growth%20by%20around%200.5%20percentage%20points%20within%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20effect%20is%20even%20stronger%20when%20financial%20markets%20are%20volatile%2C%20adding%20another%200.3%20percentage%20points%20to%20the%20slowdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b04640af-9b69-4fff-8dff-2f0804f8a443%5C%22%3EBanks%20with%20weaker%20balance%20sheets%20cut%20back%20the%20most%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20bank-level%20data%20since%202007%2C%20the%20study%20shows%20that%20lenders%20with%20less%20liquidity%20or%20more%20bad%20loans%20cut%20back%20more%20aggressively%20%E2%80%94%20shrinking%20credit%20growth%20by%20about%201%20percentage%20point%20more%20than%20healthier%20banks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstitutions%20with%20greater%20exposure%20to%20the%20US%20dollar%20also%20raised%20interest%20rates%20and%20shortened%20loan%20maturities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20drag%20is%20also%20clear%20at%20the%20company%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20firm%20data%20since%202013%2C%20the%20authors%20find%20that%20when%20US%20policy%20uncertainty%20is%20high%2C%20the%20impact%20of%20an%20ECB%20rate%20cut%20on%20business%20investment%20falls%20by%20about%2020%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20effect%20is%20most%20severe%20for%20investment-heavy%20companies%20and%20firms%20with%20strong%20trade%20links%20to%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224bba56d7-d15b-4a0c-a05b-7e7e0dc24220%5C%22%3EUncertainty%20blunts%20the%20power%20of%20rate%20cuts%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20for%20Europe%20is%20that%20uncertainty%20freezes%20decision-making%20at%20companies%20and%20banks%20and%20makes%20European%20Central%20Bank%20policy%20less%20effective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERate%20cuts%20that%20normally%20spur%20investment%20deliver%20weaker%20results%2C%20meaning%20the%20ECB%20has%20to%20act%20more%20forcefully%20to%20achieve%20the%20same%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20authors%20put%20it%2C%20US%20policy%20uncertainty%20%26quot%3Bcan%20significantly%20influence%20credit%20dynamics%2C%20business%20investment%2C%20and%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20monetary%20policy%20in%20the%20euro%20area.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-us-policy-uncertainty-is-quietly-dragging-down-european-growth-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1759489608000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68df982ccc993f9955cf72df%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-us-policy-uncertainty-is-quietly-dragging-down-european-growth-2025-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20policy%20uncertainty%20is%20cutting%20euro-area%20lending%2C%20slowing%20investment%2C%20and%20weakening%20the%20European%20Central%20Bank's%20ability%20to%20boost%20growth.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tspirlet%40insider.com%20(Thibault%20Spirlet)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A25%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.co